programmes.show_description: Shane and Russell gamble on a unique wash plant. The Poseidon Crew search for an ancient river gutter, while Jacqui and Andrew battle intense heat. S6, Ep13
Outbreak. As they approach the halfway point of their brutal challenge, the remaining survivalists face a devastating setback when deadly bacteria threaten to take out their leader. S2, Ep4
Worlds Collide Part 2. After the loss of their chief provider, the remaining five survivalists endure yet another shocking development when they learn they are not alone in the Amazon. S2, Ep5

Roanoke Shopping Center. The team heads to a local shopping centre to salvage a large, decorative frame, rolling doors and more. They also find great items from a pick in New Jersey. S9, Ep8
Country Store And Gas Station. The crew salvages an old country store. Using materials from the project, Mike and Robert create a tribute bench for a veterans' retreat. S9, Ep9
The Empire Strikes Back - Part 1. Mining empires clash in the epic battle to dominate Nome. Mr. Gold has a plan to yield 3000 ounces, while the Kellys impress a new investor. S11, Ep1
The Empire Strikes Back - Part 2. Mining empires clash in the epic battle to dominate Nome. Mr. Gold has a plan to yield 3000 ounces, while the Kellys impress a new investor. S11, Ep2
Shane is lured out of retirement to find gold on Messenger's Patch. After pushing through a dust storm, Neville is called home for hospital tests. S9, Ep9
Land Of The Brown Snake, The. First up, Julia tackles two snakes in a crowded garage. Then, she deals with an eastern brown snake, the second most venomous snake in the world. S1, Ep2
No Second Chances. When the fleet arrives on the Opi grounds a skipper regrets sending his men out in savage weather to save the boat - there are no second chances on the Bering Sea. S5, Ep9
Sea Of Misery. Three weeks in, the miserable conditions already have the crabbers turning on each other. Plus deadly ice stands between one skipper and the safety of harbour. S5, Ep10
Striking Gold. Leading to one of the richest finds in Darrell's career, the team discovers ornate artefacts that indicate the location of a 16th century captain's quarters. S2, Ep8
True Cross Of Christ. Explorer Josh Gates journeys to Jerusalem and Istanbul searching for lost pieces of the cross from the crucifixion of Jesus Christ. S2, Ep8
The Ark Of The Covenant. Josh Gates heads to Israel and Ethiopia to search for the lost Ark of the Covenant, the sacred relic said to contain the Ten Commandments. S3, Ep12
Marsh Madness. The Raneys face a swamp nightmare in Georgia. They must find an ingenious way to reclaim the Buchannans' land from a snake and gator-infested swamp. S4, Ep9
Machine Mayhem. It's the last chance for the Rookies' partnership. Meanwhile, the Cooke brothers fight busted hoses and breakdowns in their quest to strike it rich. S2, Ep6
Against All Odds. Rookie Justin struggles to get his 20-tonne excavator across an extremely busy highway. Plus, Opal Queen Kelly tackles a new challenge with a new partner. S2, Ep7
We Have Not Yet Begun to Fight. As the polar ice descends, The Saga is in danger of sinking, Jake must act fast to save his crew, and Josh gambles big-time by heading towards danger. S11, Ep18
UFOs Over New Mexico. Responding to recent UFO sightings, Josh Gates sends his team to New Mexico for a new investigation into the infamous, unsolved Socorro Landing Incident. S2, Ep8
The Gathering Storm. The team discover tree structures on different sides of the same mountain. As a storm approaches, Bryce prepares to pinpoint Bigfoot's location. S5, Ep7
Marcus and Dale find a huge gold nugget. The Gold Timers uncover their biggest gold haul ever, while Shane and Russell overwork their sluice. S6, Ep14
Divided We Fall. Days after the shocking arrival of a new team member, division among the remaining six survivalists deepens as Russell leads the men on a risky two-day hunting trek. S2, Ep6
Left Behind. A violent two-day storm descends on the jungle. Before it's over, one more survivalist will be gone, leaving another hanging by a tenuous thread. S2, Ep7

Apple Barn. The team heads to Winchester, Virginia, to salvage an abandoned orchard barn, but they must pick through years of trash and treasures before they can begin. S9, Ep10
Saving A Gem. The crew finds a gem with a log cabin tucked inside an old farmhouse, but they struggle to disassemble and demolish the property due to the ever-increasing mud. S9, Ep11
This Means War - Part 1. Two monster dredges duke it out on the Bering Sea as a war brews between Shawn and Kris. Vernon's diver bleeds on his ascent. S11, Ep3
This Means War - Part 2. Two monster dredges duke it out on the Bering Sea as a war brews between Shawn and Kris. Vernon's diver bleeds on his ascent. S11, Ep4
Jacqui and Andrew pioneer new gold-hunting ground at Fish Creek. Rookie prospector, Kat, removes an old stump from the middle of the Brumbie's lease. S9, Ep10
Fear. In Airlie Beach, Julia catches two venomous snakes and releases them back into nature. Then, her next mission is an eastern brown snake. S1, Ep3
Lockout. After battling freezing spray, colossal waves and sub-zero temperatures, it's a race to harbour to offload their haul. But the immense arctic ice pack stands in their way. S5, Ep11
See the best of the monster seas, boat-crushing ice, scary rescues, wallet-stuffing crab pots, fights, and selfless heroism from the world of Deadliest Catch.
Plummer's Gold. Josh sets off to search for the lost fortune of a notorious Montana sheriff. During his investigation, Josh blows open a mine that's been sealed for over a century. S3, Ep1
Mysteries Of Bermuda Triangle. Josh Gates dives into the mysteries of the Bermuda Triangle. He goes to the ocean floor, the skies and space to explore its intriguing disappearances. S6, Ep10
Revealing The Triangle. To conclude his epic investigation, Josh Gates uses cutting-edge technology to investigate the Bermuda Triangle's most infamous shipwreck and lost flights. S6, Ep11
Subarctic S.O.S. The Raneys answer an urgent call from central Alaska, where they find a family with all the infrastructure but minimal skills to realize their dream. S5, Ep3
Blue Fire Opal Or Bust. Justin recruits his fiancé after admitting he's facing financial disaster. Plus, the Fire Crew face deadly snakes and the Cooke Brothers go down deep. S2, Ep8
Race Against Time. The Rookies battle busted hoses and finally hit treasure. Meanwhile, at their wash plant, the Cooke Brothers race to beat the worst drought in a decade. S2, Ep9
Carpe Diem. A new face joins the fold - 23-year-old Sean Dwyer fighting for the legacy of his father. Plus, Captain Keith's life spirals, and Sig torments his old protégé. S12, Ep1
The crew fly in to treat a surfer having a heart attack. They also face a battle against the Cornish weather to rescue a pensioner in distress. S2, Ep1
The flying paramedics tend to a gardener in trouble and a patient with a unique medical history. Plus, they're faced with a worrying head injury. S2, Ep2
